      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i'm just kinda worried because the pain is a bit sharp. but honestly i've had panic attacks before and it felt pretty similar to this. u think i should maybe just take an anti-anxiety med or something to calm down so i can sleep? i don't really want to go looking for a clinic in a weird city if it's just the stress.",
